iNTRODUCTION...

   In all times, man has loved violence. There has always been something 
special about blowing someone stright to hell. Some hundred years ago it 
was less non-ok to do this with a person, but nowdays you can't even beat a 
single old lady without being punished by the law. That is why we have 
video- and computergames.
   Gravity-games has existed longer than God himself, but not until Now you
have had the time to release your anger via wAZiT - the deadly tournament!

I played some YAGG before I made this game. I noticed that it was partly
written in Blitz. As I happen to be the world's best Blitz-programmer, I 
decided to make such a game my self. I had the first beta ready half an hour
later ;) 

Anyway. Game is on, lad!



