mAIN oPTIONS...
   
   Both player can affect the cursor in this menu. So if your friend does 
something that you don't fancy, just slap him in his face with your joy.
Use joy/keyboard up/down to go up/down in menu. Press fire/<SPACE> to 
change or select current item.

   Start Game  - Go to the craft-menu.
   Arena       - Select battle arena.
                    Only 2 available in this archive. But send me an e-mail
                    if you want some more for FREE.
   Ply.1 Ctrl  - Keyboard
                    <SPACE>          - Shoot
                    Left/Right arrow - Rotate left/right
                    Down arrow       - Special weapon
               - MousePort (Joy in port 0)
                    Fire       - Shoot
                    Left/Right - Rotate left/right
                    Down       - Special weapon
   Ply.2 Ctrl  - JoyPort (Joy in port 1)
                    Fire       - Shoot
                    Left/Right - Rotate left/right
                    Down       - Special weapon
   Lives       - Amount of lives to start with. 
   Kamikaze    - Kamikaze deaths on/off.
   wAZiT Story - Read the wonderful story of wAZiT.
   Quit Game   - Exits to where-ever-the-game-was-started-from.



cRAFT oPTIONS

   There's no idea of telling you about all ships, but I can tell you what 
all them strange short words are.

   Spd - Max speed of ship.
   /   - Accelleration.
   Del - Bullet delay (low is good).
   Rot - Speed of rotation.
   Abs - Damage absorbation (high is good).

   Ehm... "Perfect" is MY favourit ship. But of cource, if I wanted to, I 
could create an immortal ship with mega-gun-power ;)



sPECIAL wEAPONS...

   Missile - A strong weapon with high speed.
   Tomi    - A rapid weapon that hurts.
   Bomb    - Falls down. Hurts very much, but is hard to aim with.
   AntiG   * Removes gravitation from your ship.
   Break   * Stops your ship in no time.
   Refill  - Use this to heal your ship.
   Warp    - Moves you to a random position.
   Elec    * Your oponent will loose life if he/she touches you.
   Magnet  - Bang your enemy to the wall by giving him this pulse.
   Homing  - Missile that flies stright to your fiend.
   Diswarp - Warps your enemy to random position.
   Circle  - Bullets all around you.
   Centre  * NAITV
   Reverse - Turn your enemie's bullets against him self (sort of).
   Turn    - NAITV
   Nuke    - NAITV
   Quake   - NAITV
   Random  - Random your enemies direction.

* = Permanent
NAITV = Not Available In This Version



